name: Robbie Rudder
text: The Military Competence Exam was great and very convenient through PHPA. My problem with this organization is that they promote Mr. Schwab to sign off on your commercial license for $80 without making it known to all applicants that this a free and easy process through any FAA FSDO. Spending $80 may be convenient for you if you won’t have an office near your duty location but you are not limited to using his services. Finally, Mr. Schwab won’t endorse a type rating for CH-47F course graduates but this rating is applied to license at your local FSDO.
